ITEM 9 1226 VAL2=3612
;scripts
IFPREVERB SIT -1
ECHO PLAYER You take a seat upon one of the cushions lining the table.
ECHO OTHERS %n takes a seat upon one of the beautiful cushions.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB MEDITATE -1
ECHO PLAYER As you begin to clear your mind you notice the crystal mirror.
ECHO PLAYER Behind its placid surface the swirling whorls of mist slowly part
ECHO PLAYER as you see a face move forward.
ECHO PLAYER A voice speaks in your mind...
ECHO PLAYER "... the heart, ... like the mirror, ... when perfectly placid
ECHO PLAYER and clear, reflects the very image of the Way ..."
ECHO OTHERS %n seems to fade briefly before becoming substantial once again.
CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PRAY -1
ECHO PLAYER You kneel down and close your eyes in silent prayer to your
ECHO PLAYER ancestors. A gentle voice whispers within your mind...
ECHO PLAYER "The Way is a void, used but never filled: An abyss it is, like
ECHO PLAYER an ancestor from which all things come. It blunts sharpness,
ECHO PLAYER resolves tangles; it tempers light, subdues turmoil. A deep pool
ECHO PLAYER it is, never to run dry..."
ECHO OTHERS %n prays to %h ancestors.
POSITION KNEEL
CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB ROAR -1
ECHO ALL The glowing sapphire eyes of the two dragon statues seem to intensify
ECHO ALL glowing blindingly bright before assuming their normal glow once
ECHO ALL again.
ENDIF
IFSAY Ulnar
ECHO ALL The fireplace seems to come to life. A flame bursts forth from the
ECHO ALL mouth of the wise looking dragon and the eyes glow bright. Soon
ECHO ALL there is a roaring fire in the fireplace.
ENDIF
